22-Sep-2009  Alexandre Trilla  <atrilla@salle.url.edu>

    * EmoLib-0.1.0
    New data structure successfully updated. The classifiers are
    separate modules in the pipeline and can be trained and saved
    into an external XML file. This system is debugged wrt the one 
    used for the Interspeech 2009 publication.


